prompts.frontCover: A charming cartoon-style watercolor illustration of a slightly frazzled, but very happy, sloth wearing a small party hat, hanging upside down from a tree branch. The sloth is holding a half-eaten slice of birthday cake with one candle still lit. Below the sloth, a group of three cheerful, brightly colored snails, also wearing tiny party hats, are racing towards a single dropped crumb of cake, leaving faint, shimmering trails behind them. The central text, "Happy Birthday... take your time celebrating," is written in a beautiful, readable, flowing handwritten cursive script in a dark teal color. The entire scene is rendered in a soft, flowing watercolor style with visible artistic brush strokes, delicate paint bleeds, and a subtle paper texture background. Flat 2D artwork.
